Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:08.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wow! I can't believe how many ponies showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:13.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I can! I mean, finding out who the Ponyville Day's Pony of Ceremonies is is a pretty big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:18.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,, I didn't know Granny Smith was on the selection committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:19.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:22.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Ponyville Day's celebrates the founding of Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and she was right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:28.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm glad the Commitee did not automatically pick me,\N so everypony gets the chance to see how great being me actually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:32.12,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Even though the festival is basically a party\Nand the Pony of Ceremonies gets to organize the whole thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:34.19,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,so it'd totally make sense if they did pick me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:37.30,Mayor,,0,0,0,,Citizens of Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:40.47,Mayor,,0,0,0,,This year's applicants were all exceptional,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:45.06,Mayor,,0,0,0,,but there can only be one Ponyville Day's Pony of Ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:47.56,Mayor,,0,0,0,,And that pony is…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.28,Mayor,,0,0,0,,…Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:00:59.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Allright, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:00.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:03.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you're gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:13.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I might have a few ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.43,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited for the festival I can hardly stand up straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:03.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Rarity was picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know she'll add a touch of elegance to the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Probably more than a touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:23.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,This year's Ponyville Day's festival, designed by Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:27.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,will feature various high-class events, such as:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:31.09,Spike,,0,0,0,,A silent cider auction and tasting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:35.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,A Ponyville Gala in town square!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:40.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,And, of course, a Ponyville fashion show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:46.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,This year's Ponyville Day's festival Pony of Ceremonies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:50.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,creates shimmering couture of her own design.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:54.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And the theme is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Small!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Chic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:00.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wow, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You really have put a lot of effort into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.68,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.92,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I think it's going to be magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.28,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:14.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's such a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But of course, I couldn't possibly do it all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The festival's in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie and I can hang lights and decorations in the town square.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:26.26,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I can get Sweet Apple Acres all ready for the cider tasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:32.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And now Twilight, if you and Fluttershy wouldn't mind helping with the fashion show?..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:37.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can focus on the thing I'm worried about most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:38.74,Somepony,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:43.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Creating a Ponyville Day's festival fantastic enough to impress…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,…Trenderhoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Who's Trenderhoof?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How can you not know who Trendehoof is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:04:02.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Trenderhoof is only the most amazing, handsomest\Ntravel writer to have ever traveled or written!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:06.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Before Las Pegasus became an Equestria travel destination, he wrote about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:10.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Before the culinary revolution in Trottingham, he discovered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:14.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,He knows what's going to be hot even before it's tepid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:18.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sounds like somepony has a little bit of a crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:23.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Crush doesn't even begin to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,He's practically divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he's comming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thank you ever so much for joining me, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could have met Trenderhoof on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:49.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't be nervous about meeting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.31,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Is that him? Is he here? Twilight, is he there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You don't suppose he has decided not to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Twilight, I don't see him!\N What if he doesn't arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The whole festival would be a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Twilight, where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,, Rarity, you have to get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean, you haven't even met him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:37.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's him! It's him! It's him! It's him! Him! It's him! It's him! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, go and talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:42.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hello mister Trenderhoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:57.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I am Rarity, and I have been chosen as pony of ceremonies for the Ponyville Days Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.59,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Please call me Trend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And over here would be the climax of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The Ponyville Days Gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:18.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Music, dancing and of course locally sourced menu of delicious treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:23.03,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Reminds me of the springfling meets Manehattan wedding I wrote about in Galloping Prance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:28.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Exactly! I can't even describe how much of/your work has influenced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:37.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And finally. Sweet Apple Acres! Ponyville's core... So to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Where our quaint little hummock began.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.95,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Breath taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.74,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I've heard about it of course. But to see it "en vérité".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.21,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,To stand on the soil of working farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.42,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,You can really feel the authenticity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh yes. Well, they really do grow apples here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:03.84,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Thank you Rarity. Thank you for bringing me here. This farm is truly something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:08.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I had planned to transform it into an elegant country inn for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:13.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But now I see just how special it is. Au naturel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.74,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Au naturel indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:25.16,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Who? Is? That?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:46.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why are you staring at her like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:49.68,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,, I've seen a lot in my travels but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:53.09,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,...I've never beheld such beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.40,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.98,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,The pony of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:07.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity? Rarity? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,I brought my cider testing cup. Are you ready to go try the samples?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:20.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What's the po-o-oint?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,Is it something like I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity, I can't hear what are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:38.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like me because he has a crush on Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:43.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Even though I had a crush on him ever since the beginning of time, and it's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,Trenderhoof doesn't like you? That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:53.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh Spike. How could you even know what it's like to be totally obsessed with the pony...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:57.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,only to find that they're obsessed somepony else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:03.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I mean, what could Applejack possibly have that I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:14.61,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,You know. I have such respect for the work ethic of Earth Ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:18.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Ah jee. Thanks. Granny Smith always said:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,"Pick an apple a day and keep trouble away".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.53,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,How many varieties of apples do you think there are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,On the farm or in all of Equestria, cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:30.19,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I once had an apple so rare they thought it was extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.55,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I ate four of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Is that a fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:42.90,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,That's my thing. I take the mundane, the simple, the unappreciated and I make it relatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you can relate to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:49.06,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Mee too. But enough about me. I wanna know about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.34,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,What do apples mean to Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:57.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're interested in Ponyville and all, but I'm kinda busy with my chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:02.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And if I can't get them done, there won't be a Ponyville Day's festival for you to write about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, that will never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:09.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rarity, what are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What, this old thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:15.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Aren't you too busy planning a festival to keep making new outfits for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But the thought of hauling apples inspired me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and I just couldn't stop myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:26.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If there's one thing I love, it's hauling apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.70,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I'm growing fond of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe you two should try it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.50,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a tad inspired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:43.36,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Without farm life there'd be such disparity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:47.40,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,These thoughts I think with great clarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:49.78,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Apples high to sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.60,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,She's the one of my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.40,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,That fruit-hauling pony named…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.83,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:07.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity, why do you wanna plow a field?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Is it me, or could this use a splash of color?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:11.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And maybe a wash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:13.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Don't we need to check on the gala decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But Trend obviously has a thing for farm life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If I can't convince him that I'm just as much of a farmhoof as Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'll never get him interested in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,The festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:25.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:29.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I do appreciate your help ever so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do a thing without you, Spikey-poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what friends are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:36.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Farm thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How does Applejack do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:49.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, it would help if the harness was on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I am simply lending a hoof for the chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Which I love doing ever so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:01.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're still interested, after the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can teach you all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:07.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But right now I need to get the plowing done, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:09.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,She makes it look so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.29,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.45,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Isn't she fantastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:30.21,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I really don't see what the fuss is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now, Rarity, you be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,If you don't get the bucking just right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,you could sprain a hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:43.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I am perfectly familiar with the applebucking process, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But, while you seem to rely on raw power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:49.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I believe a certain amount of style is required.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:52.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's really more of a dance, if you ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:05.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, your way is definitely long on style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.78,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:10.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll all excuse me, I have some more chores to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.88,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.58,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, why Trend, you can ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.42,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to ask for a while, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:29.82,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,frankly, I'm sort of embarrassed…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.11,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Rarity…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.87,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Do you… think…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.68,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Applejack would be my date for the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go ask her yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.46,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:01.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If you've come to apologize, there's really no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Let's dispense with the charade, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:09.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Listen, I know you really want Trend to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:10.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Despite somepony's best efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I swear I don't know why he is paying so much attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I don't know anypony who's that interested in farming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Not even me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:24.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well maybe it's time Trend met a real country pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:29.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be working on the festival instead of coming up with new ways to impress Trend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sure you'd love that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, I have a new vision for the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:40.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and it's gonna be more country then the whole Apple family put together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little late to be changing the theme?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm too scared to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:57.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Firstly, I just want to thank you for coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:02.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and second, I know, ya'll all adore my new festival theme!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Simple ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:24.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, what's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:28.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rarity, that is the silliest get-up I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It is a little funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you aren't serious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I'm serious
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Wha. Wouldn't I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Because you would never dress like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:46.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You like fashion and high society and fancy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:51.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I can like plowing fields and hauling apples just as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How do you know what I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Because I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:16:00.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well. Maybe you don't know me as well as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:06.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I suppose it is just a coincidence that Trenderhoof seems so interested in country life too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, then I guess I'll just have to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:18.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now. If you all will excuse me I have a hootenanny of a festival to put on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:29.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now. To be a model in the simple ways fashion show
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:32.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,you might think simple means less is more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well? That just ain't so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:39.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If you want to be real simple, more is more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:49.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now, y'all go off and make yourselves look just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:59.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who's our next model for the fashion show?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Apple… Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who the hay is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:32.07,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Wow, Rarity. What ever would make you think I was joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:35.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Because... You would never wear an ensemble like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You like plowing fields and hauling apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I can like fashion just as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you do not know me as well as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:50.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fine. But I got a whole festival to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:54.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So if y'all going to start modeling just get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:01.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Life is a festival. And you should celebrate it by looking just like me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,because I'm a trend-setting fashionista.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You are a trend-setting fashionista?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:13.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, that is a most ridiculous thing I've ever…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I mean… Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:20.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I, on other hoof, couldn't care less how I look
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:23.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,long as I get the chores done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:28.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeedy-doodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:36.01,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My mane need to be perfectly coiffed all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:41.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, my mane is full of dust and split ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:45.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My hooves are so polished you can see your reflection in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:49.86,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My hooves are cracked and dry of working in the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm so fashion-forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:54.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I wear droopy drawers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I smell like rosebuds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:00.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I love being covered in mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Goodness! Your couture!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.61,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Ooh, it's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:19.31,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Will somepony bring me a towel to wipe this repulsive filth from my hooves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,There is the Rarity I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:25.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applejack. I'm sorry I said all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:29.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You are a true friend who probably knows me better than I know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:32.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I was thinking wearing this ridiculous outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I kinda know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:38.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But you were just trying to help me see how silly I was being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:39.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:43.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Besides, that gown looks just gorgeous on you. I wish I hadn't ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.77,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I wish I hadn't ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Thanks. It's nice, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:50.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's magnificent! Wherever did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, It is one of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:59.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'll need three gallons of boling water and one ounce of detergent, stat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.97,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I'm moving to Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:09.99,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Being the most interesting pony in Equestria is exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:14.93,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,I wanna leave my exotic exciting life behind and live on a farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:15.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:21.01,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, that's real nice, but I sure hope you weren't thinking of Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:28.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Look, you're a fine pony, but, well, I'm a…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:33.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I think, what Applejack is trying to say, is that there is something unappealing about a pony
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:36.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,who changes himself so much just to impress somepony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:41.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If somepony doesn't like you for who you are, it's their loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.54,Trenderhoof,,0,0,0,,Well, this is awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:45.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:48.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,In fact, I think I know just how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:50.93,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Is it too late to go back to "Small Town Chic"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:55.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not if I can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:03.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Organizing the Ponyville Day's celebration was one of the hardest things I've ever done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I learnt an important lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:13.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Real friends will like you for who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:17.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and changing yourself to impress them is no way to make new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And, when you're as fabulous as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,it's practically a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:59.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon2anon\Nsunnysubs.com
